  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At level 15, you become the representation of the ideal Geisha, earning the prestigious title of Tayu, one of the highest and most respected titles in the Clan.<br />No Geisha, except for the Okiya and matrons stands above you, and even the matrons deeply respect you, considering you the most precious girl in the Clan, to be protected at all costs.<br />As a result, you are granted access to every social event, with no one daring to refuse your presence. Even high nobles or leaders will find it difficult to decline your esteemed attendance.<br />Additionally, you can now use your \"Come My Champion\" Trait without needing a rest or suffering any repercussions. Your bodyguard will return fully healed with max HP and chakra, and will not suffer exhaustion after combat.<br />You can use this ability once per long rest.<br />Furthermore, you gain advantage on any Charisma saving throws you are subjected to.<br />Your natural beauty transcends mortal limitations, increasing your Charisma maximum by 2 and boosting your current Charisma by 2 as well.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
